    <entry>
      <title>butterfly 使用过程中遇到的一些小问题</title>
      <link href="/2022/10/27/blog6/"/>
      <url>/2022/10/27/blog6/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="\js\Meting.min.js"></script><h2 id="在线聊天"><a href="#在线聊天" class="headerlink" title="在线聊天"></a>在线聊天</h2><p>打开<code>chatra</code>功能以后我发现鼠标经过的时候不显示在线聊天,而是显示<code>rightside.chat.btn</code><br><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/2022/10/27/blog6/1.jpg"><br>解决方法: 打开路径<code>node_modules\hexo-theme-butterfly\languages</code><br><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/2022/10/27/blog6/2.jpg"><br>因为我用的是<code>zh-CN</code>,所以修改<code>zh-CN.yml</code></p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/2022/10/27/blog6/3.jpg"></p><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">chat_btn:</span> <span class="string">在线聊天</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>hexo s</code>以后,重新刷新页面即可看到修改成功<br><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/2022/10/27/blog6/4.jpg"></p><h2 id="文章链接不正确"><a href="#文章链接不正确" class="headerlink" title="文章链接不正确"></a>文章链接不正确</h2><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/2022/10/27/blog6/5.jpg"><br>解决方法: 修改根目录下的<code>_config.yml</code><br><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/2022/10/27/blog6/6.jpg"></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">url: http://lmxyz.xyz</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>hexo s</code>重新部署即可<br><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="/2022/10/27/blog6/7.jpg"></p>]]></content>
      
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> hexo </category>
          
      </categories>
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> butterfly </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
